好似有朋友有睇開 夜d幫你問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmk有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deff4c09c452b546ff87f494cb6944eec2beb776","tid":11194,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脊醫係類似順勢療法，無任何科學實證<br />\n背脊有事最好睇專科/物理治療/甚至跌打都好過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為脊醫就係專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該帶佢睇咩？去正苦門診？"},{"pid":"a32ec58d2cae4ccf6c434a97f313b3010457d9d3","tid":11194,"uid":38449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>脊醫係類似順勢療法，無任何科學實證<br />\n背脊有事最好睇專科/物理治療/甚至跌打都好過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為脊醫就係專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該帶佢睇咩？去正苦門診？</blockquote><br />\n急唔急先<br />\n正苦轉介加排期分分就有排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係可以試下正苦門診睇完再決定要去咩專科再自己去睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043919232eda2eeaaa25ed489038e501d52f0d28","tid":11194,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>脊醫係類似順勢療法，無任何科學實證<br />\n背脊有事最好睇專科/物理治療/甚至跌打都好過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為脊醫就係專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該帶佢睇咩？去正苦門診？</blockquote><br />\n急唔急先<br />\n正苦轉介加排期分分就有排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係可以試下正苦門診睇完再決定要去咩專科再自己去睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係大脾前面痛 我上網搵過係關背面神經線事 唔係肌肉痛<br />\n<br />\n當然我想愈快愈好啦 正苦門診要排幾耐？定係睇普通西醫轉介都得？"},{"pid":"3d644ec6ae747d7ac7af8687b0a2774d92b77007","tid":11194,"uid":38449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>脊醫係類似順勢療法，無任何科學實證<br />\n背脊有事最好睇專科/物理治療/甚至跌打都好過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為脊醫就係專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該帶佢睇咩？去正苦門診?</blockquote><br />\n急唔急先<br />\n正苦轉介加排期分分就有排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係可以試下正苦門診睇完再決定要去咩專科再自己去睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係大脾前面痛 我上網搵過係關背面神經線事 唔係肌肉痛<br />\n<br />\n當然我想愈快愈好啦 正苦門診要排幾耐？定係睇普通西醫轉介都得？</blockquote><br />\n係咪脊醫/所謂脊骨神經科既網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其本上佢地既theory 係所有病都係由脊骨起咁滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685ff07f537abf792887912f90cbfebcb6bcfbcc","tid":11194,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>脊醫係類似順勢療法，無任何科學實證<br />\n背脊有事最好睇專科/物理治療/甚至跌打都好過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以為脊醫就係專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該帶佢睇咩？去正苦門診?</blockquote><br />\n急唔急先<br />\n正苦轉介加排期分分就有排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係可以試下正苦門診睇完再決定要去咩專科再自己去睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係大脾前面痛 我上網搵過係關背面神經線事 唔係肌肉痛<br />\n<br />\n當然我想愈快愈好啦 正苦門診要排幾耐？定係睇普通西醫轉介都得？</blockquote><br />\n係咪脊醫/所謂脊骨神經科既網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其本上佢地既theory 係所有病都係由脊骨起咁滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 好似係台灣網<br />\n同埋佢同事都試過類似情況 係背脊神經線出事<br />\n要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都有叫佢睇佢同事個醫生"},{"pid":"5ecfd4ddd5bdf5df199076163581c9c23106429f","tid":11194,"uid":38449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n唔係 好似係台灣網<br />\n同埋佢同事都試過類似情況 係背脊神經線出事<br />\n要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都有叫佢睇佢同事個醫生</blockquote><br />\n咁不如睇左普通正苦門診先，唔使好耐<br />\n耐係排期正苦專科"},{"pid":"dc92afee614e98d4592f531c5769789b166fb7c7","tid":11194,"uid":13076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"睇開銅鑼灣既chiropractor L.Wong<br />\n佢師父好掂但退左休<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好唔好自己試過至知<br />\n唔賣廣告 有心google會搵到<br />\n<br />\n祝福樓主媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8917ed90092395980d1781acf183c2bbea4ca6","tid":11194,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔係 好似係台灣網<br />\n同埋佢同事都試過類似情況 係背脊神經線出事<br />\n要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都有叫佢睇佢同事個醫生</blockquote><br />\n咁不如睇左普通正苦門診先，唔使好耐<br />\n耐係排期正苦專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 岩岩排左聽日睇 起碼初步睇下咩事先"},{"pid":"7d6faa8e1f7f522e8dff111403d2e0d35fe1384f","tid":11194,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇開銅鑼灣既chiropractor L.Wong<br />\n佢師父好掂但退左休<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好唔好自己試過至知<br />\n唔賣廣告 有心google會搵到<br />\n<br />\n祝福樓主媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等陣google下"},{"pid":"3ad097560fb86b97b99569b5123c445e8b8af0a7","tid":11194,"uid":11918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"自己睇開<br />\n我會話係有系統嘅跌打推拿，鬆骨程度比推拿高，亦會運用針灸等，視乎情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/184905_8842d9b9c13e38ea8e4c703ae358fb37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F